      "camp": "Persistent infrastructure that stays in tableau.",
      "zone_use": "Activated in a matching zone to convert a tool into food, safety, or rescue progress.",
      "recovery": "Immediate one-time effect; discarded after use."
    },
    "loop": "Most payoff should come from using crafted tools in the correct place, not from drawing it directly.",
    "cook_bonus": "Food cards may be eaten directly in a pinch, but crafted food systems should do the real work."
  },
